ento 2 03\",\"className\":\"wp-image-1413 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"3\"}</script></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To enable this feature, follow these steps:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Go to your Magento store&#8217;s admin panel.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Navigate to Store &gt; Configuration &gt; Catalog.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Under the Catalog tab, click on Catalog.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>In the Storefront section, locate the fields labeled &#8220;Use Flat Catalog Category&#8221; and &#8220;Use Flat Catalog Product&#8221; and change them to &#8220;Yes.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Minimize and optimize Javascript and CSS.</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Excessive use of Javascript and CSS can also contribute to slow performance in Magento 2. To address this issue, you can minimize the use of Javascript and CSS.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained wp-image-1414 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\"><div style=\"max-width:1024px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20height=&#x27;566&#x27;%20width=&#x27;1024&#x27;%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;position:static\"/></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" data-placeholder-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%\"></div><img data-gatsby-image-ssr=\"\" data-wp-inline-image=\"4\" data-main-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;transform:translateZ(0);transition:opacity 250ms linear;width:100%;will-change:opacity;opacity:0\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/_gatsby/image/ea020c87e0324c49ac14924cb56e3f32/b2e5b2fdda3e5386d4241f91f3d22999